data.text:
Want to travel from Newhaven Harbour to Newhaven Town by train? Start your journey with us.

The train from Newhaven Harbour to Newhaven Town usually takes 2 minutes on average to travel 0 miles (1 km), although the quickest services can take as little as 2 minutes. You can expect to find 19 trains per day running on this popular route. Good news! There are direct trains available to Newhaven Town, so you can just make yourself comfortable as soon as you board the train and just enjoy the journey. All or part of your journey will be served by Southern, as they are the main operator of trains on this route.

You can save money on train tickets from Newhaven Harbour to Newhaven Town if you book in advance, travel Off-Peak – tickets are usually cheaper during quieter times on weekdays and weekends – or get a Railcard and save up to 1/3 on eligible journeys for a whole year. Use our Journey Planner at the top of the page to compare ticket prices and get the cheapest fares.

If you want to know more about the journey, scroll up for timetables and live train times, or keep reading for tips on finding cheap tickets and FAQs. Want to go straight to booking? Start a search with us today!
